%20and%20get%20them%20ready%20for%20school%20and%20cook%20breakfast%20and%20just%20be%20the%20family%20that%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Oberlin%2C%2036%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20mom%20of%20three%20moved%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-texas-to-las-vegas-with-family-worth-it-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETexas%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-panama-from-us-for-retirement-cost-pros-cons-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPanama%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOberlin's%20husband%20had%20served%20in%20the%20Army%20for%2012%20years%2C%20so%20her%20family%20was%20used%20to%20moving%2C%20but%20she%20said%20it%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20both%20her%20and%20her%20husband%20to%20be%20fully%20present%20for%20their%20kids.%20They%20began%20researching%20affordable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-us-to-uk-culture-surprises-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edestinations%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-spain-from-us-lower-stress-cost-of-living-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eabroad%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20they%20could%20get%20by%20without%20working%20while%20their%20kids%20were%20in%20school%2C%20and%20they%20ultimately%20settled%20on%20Panama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20really%20just%2C%20how%20can%20we%20do%20what%20we%20want%20to%20do%20for%20our%20family%20properly%3F%20And%20so%20we%20knew%20leaving%20the%20States%20would%20give%20us%20the%20opportunity%20to%20live%20off%20of%20what%20we%20had%2C%20where%20we%20could%20just%20be%20present%20with%20our%20kids%2C%26quot%3B%20Oberlin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20spoke%20to%20three%20moms%20who%20moved%20abroad%20with%20their%20families.%20They%20described%20the%20unique%20challenges%20that%20accompany%20moving%20to%20a%20new%20country%20with%20younger%20kids%2C%20espec