nk%20it's%20more%20globally%20aware%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d0cc376-0bc6-474c-a701-ec8265557872%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaryland%20to%20New%20Zealand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elissa%20Johnsen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6878f9daf748d8c055f5c815%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElissa%20Johnsen%20said%20her%20kids%20are%20better%20off%20after%20moving%20to%20New%20Zealand%20from%20the%20US.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Elissa%20Johnsen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20went%20into%20Elissa%20Johnsen's%20decision%20to%20move%20from%20Maryland%20to%20New%20Zealand%20in%202022.%20Johnsen%20was%20working%20as%20a%20nurse%20during%20the%20start%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20which%20took%20a%20severe%20mental%20toll.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20there%20was%20a%20school%20shooting%20at%20the%20high%20school%20right%20next%20to%20her%20daughter's%20elementary%20school%20in%202020%2C%20and%20Johnsen%20said%20the%20frequent%20lockdown%20drills%20were%20weighing%20her%20daughter%20down%20emotionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20that%20time%2C%20Johnsen%20said%20she%20received%20a%20recruiting%20email%20from%20a%20New%20Zealand-based%20agency%20looking%20for%20nurses.%20While%20it%20initially%20seemed%20like%20an%20unattainable%20dream%2C%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20started%20seriously%20considering%20the%20offer%2C%20and%20they%20ultimately%20made%20the%20move%20when%20her%20youngest%20child%20was%2011%20months%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20we%20read%20about%20New%20Zealand%20felt%20like%20a%20dream%2C%20the%20natural%20beauty%2C%20the%20cultural%20values%2C%20the%20emphasis%20on%20work-life%20balance%2C%20and%20a%20school%20system%20that%20seemed%20to%20put%20child%20well-being%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnsen%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20kids%20are%20now%204%2C%205%2C%20and%2010%2C%20and%20she%20said%20that%20the%20school%20system%20in%20New%20Zealand%20is%20more%20well-rounded%20than%20the%20US.%20Johnsen%20said%20that%20the%20preschools%20follow%20a%20%26quot%3Bplay-based%20curriculum%26quot%3B%20built%20on%20well-being%20and%20relationships.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20primary%20school%20still%20follows%20core%20curriculum%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20balanced%20with%20outdoor%20play%2C%20culturally%20responsive%20teaching%2C%20and%20a%20whole-child%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20someone%20who's%20now%20seen%20both%20systems%20up%20close%2C%20I'm%20struck%20by%20how%20much%20more%20relaxed%20and%20emotionally%20safe%20my%20younger%20two%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnsen%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20they're%20actually%20getting%20a%20childhood%2C%20something%20my%20oldest%2C%20in%20her%20early%20U.S.%20school%20years%2C%20missed%20out%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExpenses%20in%20New%20Zealand%20also%20aren't%20as%20burdensome%20as%20they%20were%20in%20the%20US.%20Johnsen%20said%20she%20takes%20home%20more%20of%20her%20paycheck%20and%20has%20affordable%20health%20insurance%2C%20and%20day%20care%20is%20significantly%20more%20affordable.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20she%20said%20she%20was%20quoted%20%241%2C500%20per%20child%20for%20part-time%20day%20care%2C%20while%20she%20gets%2020%20hours%20of%20free%20childcare%20in%20New%20Zealand%20a%20week.%20While%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20New%20Zealand%20is%20comparable%20to%20what%20she%20paid%20in%20the%20US%2C%20lower%20childcare%20and%20insurance%20costs%20make%20it%20manageable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20important%20to%20say%20that%20this%20choice%20isn't%20easy%20or%20cheap%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnsen%20said.%20%26quot%3BMoving%20across%20the%20world%20with%20three%20young%20kids%20meant%20letting%20go%20of%20everything%20familiar%20and%20building%20a%20life%20from%20the%20ground%20up.%20We%20questioned%