gan%20Johnson%20used%20to%20brand%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-bryan-johnson-home-netflix-doc-dont-die-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENetflix%20documentary%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbryan-johnson-anti-aging-blueprint-olive-oil-longevity-braintree-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproducts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-bryan-johnson-dont-die-summit-singapore-longevity-health-biohacking-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eevents%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYears%20ago%2C%20I%20did%20a%20thought%20experiment%20imagining%20myself%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20people%20from%20the%2025th%20century.%20It%20seemed%20obvious%20that%20they'd%20say%20Don't%20Die%20is%20how%20humanity%20saved%20itself%20and%20merged%20with%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20wrote%20in%20an%20X%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%2C%20however%2C%20says%20he's%20beginning%20to%20see%20how%20running%20a%20longevity-focused%20business%20may%20not%20mesh%20with%20preaching%20a%20religion%20on%20the%20same%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20I%20am%20so%20close%20to%20either%20shutting%20it%20down%20or%20selling%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Drummond%2C%20adding%20that%20he's%20%26quot%3Bbeen%20talking%20to%20people%20about%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20need%20the%20money%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20pain-in-the-ass%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20said%20he%20started%20the%20business%20because%20his%20friends%20were%20asking%20him%20for%20the%20health%20supplements%20he%20was%20taking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20evolved%20in%20a%20way%20where%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20do%20people%20a%20solid.%20The%20problem%20is%20now%20people%20see%20the%20business%20and%20give%20me%20less%20credibility%20on%20the%20philosophy%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20make%20that%20trade-off.%20It%20is%20not%20worth%20it%20to%20me.%20So%20yeah%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%20that%20Blueprint%20was%20facing%20problems%20with%20its%20finances.%20The%20story%20was%20published%20in%20March%20and%20was%20based%20on%20interviews%20with%20current%20and%20former%20employees%20as%20well%20as%20court%20records%20and%20internal%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Times'%20said%20in%20its%20reporting%20that%20Blueprint%20was%20missing%20its%20break-even%20point%20by%20at%20least%20%241%20million%20a%20month.%20It%20added%20that%20Johnson%20had%20told%20executives%20that%20Blueprint%20was%20running%20out%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20told%20Wired%20that%20Blueprint%20isn't%20in%20%26quot%3Bsome%20kind%20of%20emergency%20financial%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20break-even%2C%20and%20I've%20said%20that%20publicly%20many%20times.%20We've%20had%20profitable%20months%2C%20we've%20had%20loss%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbryan-johnson-does-not-want-run-blueprint-anymore-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753158463000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687eef023d5881a51c1db992%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbryan-johnson-does-not-want-run-blueprint-anymore-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20don't%20need%20the%20money%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20pain-in-the-ass%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said%20of%20Blueprint.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUr