e%20days%20before%20I%20was%20set%20to%20fly%2C%20they%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20have%20any%20budget%20for%20this%20internship%2C%20or%20any%20additional%20head%20count%20for%20that%20matter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wrote%20in%20my%20email%20that%20I%20was%20open%20to%20discussing%20this%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20want%20to%20continue%20this%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20already%20booked%20a%20flight%20to%20New%20York%2C%20paid%20for%20rent%2C%20and%20found%20a%20roommate%20to%20share%20it%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20on%20a%20bus%20crossing%20the%20Bay%20Bridge%20when%20the%20email%20came%20in.%20I%20sent%20a%20goofy%20selfie%20to%20my%20sister%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BGuess%20who's%20unemployed%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20But%20within%20minutes%2C%20reality%20hit%20me%2C%20and%20I%20started%20crying%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20bus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20called%20my%20parents%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20roommate.%20They%20were%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BJust%20go%20to%20New%20York%20and%20have%20fun.%26quot%3B%20They%20insisted%20on%20supporting%20me%20in%20following%20through%2C%20and%20now%20I'm%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e458e00e-8ee0-4553-9641-adfcd9c7211d%5C%22%3EStraight%20off%20the%20plane%20and%20into%20networking%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20on%20my%20own%2C%20and%20I%20searched%20for%20things%20to%20do%20in%20New%20York%2C%20specifically%20in%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20two%20weeks%20were%20pretty%20rough.%20I%20hopped%20around%20during%20New%20York%20Tech%20Week%2C%20which%20began%20the%20day%20I%20landed.%20I%20dropped%20off%20my%20bags%20and%20went%20straight%20from%20JFK%20Airport%20to%20IBM's%20office%2C%20running%20on%20zero%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%2C%20I%20juggled%20different%20events%2C%20met%20different%20people%2C%20and%20networked%2C%20trying%20to%20get%20my%20foot%20in%20the%20door%20and%20establish%20myself%20in%20the%20city.%20I%20signed%20up%20for%20probably%20over%2060%20events%20in%20the%20span%20of%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20week%2C%20I%20attended%20a%20crypto%20conference.%20I%20met%20a%20part-time%20blockchain%20builder%20and%20part-time%20professor%20from%20Stanford%2C%20who%20offered%20to%20circulate%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20that%20time%2C%20I%20had%20already%20applied%20to%20around%2050%20companies%20and%20asked%20at%20least%2020%20people%20in%20my%20network%20to%20share%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20portfolio%2C%20hoping%20to%20find%20anyone%20who%20might%20be%20hiring%20%E2%80%94%20a%20long%20shot%20since%20it%20was%20already%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20Stanford%20professor%20and%20folks%20in%20my%20blockchain%20club%2C%20I%20interviewed%20with%20six%20companies%2C%20and%20I%20really%20connected%20with%20a%20founder%20from%20Axal%2C%20an%20Andressen%20Horowitz-backed%20crypto%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20our%20first%20interview%2C%20he%20messaged%20me%20at%203%20a.m.%20on%20a%20Friday%20with%20the%20files%20for%20the%20take-home%20assignment.%20I%20was%20already%20awake%2C%20working%2C%20so%20I%20dove%20right%20in.%20Over%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20I%20pulled%20all-nighters%20designing%2C%20coding%2C%20and%20engineering%20the%20interface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20final%20interview%20on%20Monday%2C%20I%20walked%20him%20through%20my%20design%20process%2C%20code%2C%20repository%2C%20and%20everything%20I%20built.%20He%20offered%20me%20the%20role%20on%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20went%20back%20and%20forth%20a%20bit%20on%20compensation%2C%20but%20things%20went%20smoothly.%20I%20got%20the%20official%20offer%20in%20my%20inbox%2C%20and%20this%20time%2C%20I%20signed%20it%20for%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20their%20fastest%20hire%20ever%2C%20from%20first%20contact%20to%20offer%20in%20just%20four%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20chain%20of%20networking%20that%20put%20me%20in%20the%20position%20to%20even%20interview%20for%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20happening%20literally%20within%20two%20weeks%20of%20me%20landing%20in%20New%20York%20with%20no%20job%2C%20no%20backup%20plan%2C%20still%20feels%20incredibly%20surreal%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224ccde4de-b4b1-44a7-8546-ee652652ea2d%5C%22%3ESummer%20motto%3A%20I%20have%20nothing%20else%20to%20lose%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20really%20difficult%20to%20turn%20my%20mindset%20from%20being%20disappointed%2C%20anxious%2C%20and%20stressed%20to%20%26quot%3BI'll%20just%20take%20whatever%20life%20gives%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccepting%20and%20embracing%20that%20reality%20has%20helped%20me%20so%20much%20because%20that%20allowed%20me%20to%20not%20withhold%20any%20of%20my%20energy%20or%20hold%20back%20when%20I%20go%20to%20networking%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20nothing%20else%20to%20lose%20%E2%80%94%20that%20has%20been%20the%20motto%20of%20my%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20so%20happy%20I%20came%20to%20New%20York%20to%20meet%20the%20people%20I%20met%20and%20be%20part%20of%20the%20opportunities%20I've%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20who%20are%20older%20than%20me%20always%20tell%20me%20success%20comes%20in%20different%20ways%2C%20and%20I've%20always%20found%20it%20so%20corny.%20I%20truly%20believe%20that%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsummer-intern-lost-job-new-york-network-tech-week-hustle-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753142402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687dfeb785e81483682e589c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsummer-intern-lost-job-new-york-network-tech-week-hustle-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aaron%20Chen%20lost%20his%20internship%20after%20talking%20pay.%20He%20went%20to%20NYC%20anyway%20and%20landed%20a%20new%20role%20in%20two%20weeks%2C%20thanks%20to%20networking%20hard.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cmlee%40insider.c