ocial%20media%20platform%20and%20toward%20the%20creator%20economy.%20It%20introduced%20a%20shoppable%20collage%20feature%20that%20creators%20could%20use%20across%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20particularly%20Substack%20newsletters.%20Creators%20could%20easily%20integrate%20affiliate-marketing%20links%20using%20Zeen's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20products%20in%20many%20different%20iterations%20through%20Landing%20and%20through%20Zeen%2C%20and%20we%20hoped%20that%20this%20would%20be%20something%20that%20we%20could%20grow%20into%20a%20much%20bigger%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Buckland%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20a%20long-lasting%2C%20profitable%20social%20media%20platform%20isn't%20an%20easy%20game.%20That's%20one%20reason%20some%20investors%20have%20backed%20away%20from%20the%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20social%20media%20darlings%20have%20faced%20fates%20of%20either%20dwindling%20popularity%20or%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20shutting%20down%20entirely.%20For%20instance%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-instagram-hires-core-team-buzzy-social-media-app-poparazzi-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPoparazzi%2C%20a%20photo-sharing%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20a%20viral%20hit%20in%202021%2C%20announced%20it%20would%20shut%20down%20in%202023.%20Meanwhile%2C%20some%20creator%20economy%20startups%20have%20also%20had%20to%20face%20shutdowns%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-creator-plus-film-studio-pursues-sale-winds-down-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efilm%20studio%20Creator%2B%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20made%20the%20decision%20that%20now%20was%20the%20time%20to%20shut%20it%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Buckland%20said.%20%26quot%3BFundraising%20or%20becoming%20profitable%2C%20they%20weren't%20viable%20pathways%20for%20us%20at%20this%20point.%20It's%20a%20sad%20decision%2C%20honestly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20arti